ZH: 我们跟着地图顺着路走。
EN: We followed the map and walked along the road.

ZH: 他顺着长江一直走到了上海。
EN: He followed the Yangtze River all the way to Shanghai.

ZH: 请顺着这条走廊走到尽头。
EN: Please walk along this corridor to the end.

ZH: 她顺着我的指示找到了目的地。
EN: She found the destination by following my instructions.

ZH: 这条黄河顺着青藏高原流淌。
EN: This Yellow River flows along the Qinghai-Tibet Plateau.

ZH: 我们顺着山脉攀爬到了峰顶。
EN: We climbed to the peak along the mountain range.

ZH: 他沿着海岸线顺着风向奔驰。
EN: He rushed along the coastline with the wind.

ZH: 我们沿着街道顺着人流走。
EN: We walked along the street following the crowd.

ZH: 请顺着红色箭头前进。
EN: Please move forward along the red arrow.

ZH: 我们缓缓顺着石梯下坡。
EN: We slowly descended along the stone steps.

ZH: 他们顺着森林小道走失了。
EN: They got lost walking along the forest trail.

ZH: 请顺着这条小路前往目的地。
EN: Please go to the destination along this path.

ZH: 他们顺着歌声找到了音乐会的地点。
EN: They found the location of the concert by following the singing.

ZH: 我们靠近山脚顺着崎岖的小路攀爬。
EN: We approached the foot of the mountain and climbed along the rugged path.

ZH: 顺着这条河流你会抵达一个美丽的小村庄。
EN: You will reach a beautiful village by following this river.

ZH: 请顺着直线前进直到看到标志牌。
EN: Please go straight ahead until you see a sign.

ZH: 我们顺着瀑布走到了山洞口。
EN: We walked along the waterfall and arrived at the entrance of the cave.

ZH: 他们顺着森林的边缘行进。
EN: They proceeded along the edge of the forest.

ZH: 顺着这条路走，你会发现美丽的花园。
EN: Follow this path, and you will discover a beautiful garden.

ZH: 请靠边顺着马路行驶。
EN: Please drive along the road and keep to the side.
